      "result": "{\"meta\": null, \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"{\\\"total_count\\\":9,\\\"incomplete_results\\\":false,\\\"items\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":4808364260,\\\"number\\\":50,\\\"state\\\":\\\"closed\\\",\\\"state_reason\\\":\\\"completed\\\",\\\"locked\\\":false,\\\"title\\\":\\\"log_prob 的计算问题\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"在 https://github.com/hiyouga/EasyR1/blob/51001bd457f4fbab0055b6a07341c4ac468b61e6/verl/utils/torch_functional.py#L67 中，计算 log_prob 的函数为：\\\\n```\\\\ndef log_probs_from_logits(logits: torch.Tensor, labels: torch.Tensor) -\\\\u003e torch.Tensor:\\\\n    ...\\\\n    if FLAH_ATTN_CROSS_ENTROPY_LOSS_AVAILABLE:\\\\n        output = log_probs_from_logits_flash_attn(logits, labels)\\\\n    else:  # fall back to torch kernel, upcast logits to fp32\\\\n        output = F.cross_entropy(logits.float(), labels, reduction=\\\\\\\"none\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n    return output.view(*batch_dim)\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n当 if 触发的时候，输出：\\\\n```\\\\n@torch_og9q.compiler.disable()\\\\ndef log_probs_from_logits_flash_attn(logits: torch.Tensor, labels: torch.Tensor) -\\\\u003e torch.Tensor:\\\\n    output = cross_entropy_loss(logits, labels, inplace_backward=True)\\\\n    if not isinstance(output, tuple):\\\\n        raise ValueError(\\\\n            \\\\\\\"please make sure flash-attn\\\\u003e=2.4.3 where cross_entropy_loss returns Tuple[losses, z_losses].\\\\\\\"\\\\n        )\\\\n\\\\n    return -output[0]\\\\n```\\\\n当else触发则返回：\\\\n```\\\\noutput = F.cross_entropy(logits.float(), labels, reduction=\\\\\\\"none\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n    return output.view(*batch_dim)\\\\n```\\\\n这里的正负号好像有一些问题？cross_entropy一般得到的是 loss，应该是返回非负数的？\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",