:\\\"completed\\\",\\\"locked\\\":false,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Issue : Consider Adding Type Hints for Function Arguments in `protocol.py`\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Adding type hints to the function arguments in `protocol.py` can improve code readability and maintainability. While some arguments already have type hints, extending this to all arguments would provide a more consistent and comprehensive benefit. For example, add type hints to arguments such as `features` in `batch_collate` function or `data_items` in `collate_fn` function to improve type safety and make the function signature more explicit.\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/owner}{/repo}\\\",\\\"subscriptions_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"comments\\\":0,\\\"closed_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T09:03:08Z\\\",\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T09:03:07Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T09:03:08Z\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/EasyR1/issues/44\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/EasyR1/issues/44\\\",\\\"comments_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/EasyR1/issues/44/comments\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/EasyR1/issues/44/events\\\",\\\"labels_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/EasyR1/issues/44/labels{/name}\\\",\\\"repository_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/EasyR1\\\",\\\"reactions\\\":{\\\"total_count\\\":0,\\\"+1\\\":0,\\\"-1\\\":0,\\\"laugh\\\":0,\\\"confused\\\":0,\\\"heart\\\":0,\\\"hooray\\\":0,\\\"rocket\\\":0,\\\"eyes\\\":0,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/EasyR1/issues/44/reactions\\\"},\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"I_kwDOTNUXf88AAAABHpnOFQ\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4808357337,\\\"number\\\":39,\\\"state\\\":\\\"open\\\",\\\"locked\\\":false,\\\"title\\\":\\\"GRPO训练速度问题\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"用Qwen2.5-VL-7B模型训练GRPO，每条训练数据的输入为8张336*336的图片，加一段长度不超过1000的文本。8张A100 80G，800条训练数据10个epoch，显示需要26～30个小时，请问这个训练速度正常吗？是否有提升训练速度的方案？（训练过程中出现GPU利用率很低（20%左右），CPU利用率很高的情况）期待您的回答，非常感谢！\\\\n\\\\n参数设置如下：\\\\npython3 -m verl.trainer.main \\\\\\\\\\\\n    config=examples/config.yaml \\\\\\\\\\\\n    data.train_files=${TRAIN_PATH} \\\\\\\\\\\\n    data.val_files=${VAL_PATH} \\\\\\\\\\\\n    data.rollout_batch_size=16 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.actor.global_batch_size=16 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    data.val_batch_size=16 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.actor.model.model_path=${MODEL_PATH} \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.rollout.limit_images=8 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    trainer.experiment_name=${EXP_NAME} \\\\\\\\\\\\n    trainer.n_gpus_per_node=8 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    trainer.save_checkpoint_path=${CKPT_PATH} \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.rollout.n=8 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    trainer.logger=['console','tensorboard'] \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.actor.micro_batch_size_per_device_for_experience=16 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.actor.micro_batch_size_per_device_for_update=4 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.rollout.tensor_parallel_size=2 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.rollout.gpu_memory_utilization=0.6 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.reward.reward_type=sequential \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.reward.reward_function=./examples/reward_function/r1v.py:compute_score \\\\\\\\\\\\n    data.max_prompt_length=5120 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    worker.rollout.max_num_batched_tokens=7168 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    trainer.val_freq=50 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    trainer.save_freq=50 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    trainer.save_limit=15 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    data.max_pixels=112896 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    data.min_pixels=112896 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    trainer.total_epochs=10 \\\\\\\\\\\\n    trainer.val_before_train=false \\\\\\\\\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/owner}{/repo}\\\",\\\"subscriptions_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"comments\\\":0,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T09:01:00Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\